{"title":"希望——有感于北京正义路一号","authors":["刘滨"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":1,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望——有感于北京正义路一号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是戏剧性的安排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是必然的“巧遇”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理，终于在这儿主持正义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，搀扶着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬眉吐气的共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过了冬季；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在正义大街与真理相逢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲愤与欢欣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却化作无声的饮泣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被告席上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押进来了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴险、残忍、诬陷、阿谀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耻辱柱下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉上去了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪婪、疯狂、虚伪、卑鄙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看被告席上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十张死灰一般的脸吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的祖国十年漫长的记忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，历史庄严地捧起了起诉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起我的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年血泪浸泡的大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让过去和未来都来旁听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当专制和愚昧通奸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样把灾难孕育；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而当正义从封建桎梏中解脱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理便会告诉人民："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有你，才能推动历史！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}